	/////////////
	/*This script is to remove red field styling that is a result of when approved end date is before planned end date. Since planned end date is calculated, sometimes the system will add a couple hours which makes this true. By resetting the field value in the approved to match the planned  (to the same value) after initial save this ref field styling goes away as now approved is not before planned
	https://docs.servicenow.com/bundle/paris-it-business-management/page/product/project-management/task/t_CreateAProject.html
	*/
	////////////

	var encQueryProject = 'sys_class_nameINjavascript:getValidProjectClasses()^sys_created_onONToday@javascript:gs.beginningOfToday()@javascript:gs.endOfToday()';

	
	var grProj = new GlideRecord('pm_project');
	grProj.addEncodedQuery(encQueryProject);
	grProj.query();
	while(grProj.next()){
		grProj.approved_end_date = grProj.end_date;
		grProj.update();
	}
	


})(source, map, log, target);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_transform_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-06-12 21:47:58</sys_created_on><sys_id>b4641b041bb874107d21ebd5624bcbe3</sys_id><sys_mod_count>11</sys_mod_count><sys_name>onAfter</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_transform_script_b4641b041bb874107d21ebd5624bcbe3</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-06-13 08:37:08</sys_updated_on><when>onAfter</when></sys_transform_script></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_transform_map"><sys_transform_map action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><copy_empty_fields>false</copy_empty_fields><create_new_record_on_empty_coalesce_fields>false</create_new_record_on_empty_coalesce_fields><enforce_mandatory_fields>No</enforce_mandatory_fields><name>Project Data Load</name><order>50</order><run_business_rules>true</run_business_rules><run_script>true</run_script><script><![CDATA[(function transformRow(source, target, map, log, isUpdate) {

    /*
	This tranform map script will create short desciptions for project and tasks using lowest level application and capability - there will be a unique short description for the project and each of its project tasks
	*/

    //set these for MVP date project being created in UI mapped fields
    target.allow_dates_outside_schedule = '1';
    target.project_schedule_date_format = 'date';
    target.calculation_type = 'manual';
	target.duration = '0';


    //the rest of this script is to create one project with 3 tasks if data is correct in source row
    var app = '';
    var ca = '';
    var fs = source.u_future_state_system.toString();
    var sd = false;

    //find lowest level application in the row
	app = getApp(source.u_application_name, source.u_ditpr_don_system_acroynm, source.u_uii_acronym);
    //gs.log('mayfield ' + app);

    //find lowest level capability in the row
	ca = getCapability(source.u_capability___2_requirement_ , source.u_capability___3_requirement_, source.u_capability___4_requirement_);
    //gs.log('mayfield ' + ca);

    //create short descriptions to be used for project and tasks
    if (app != '' && ca != '' && fs != '') {
        var sdProj = ca + ' capability for application ' + app + ' conversion to ' + fs;
        var sdPTmodern = 'MODERNIZATION: ' + ca + ' capability for application ' + app + ' conversion to ' + fs;
        var sdPTdecom = 'DATA MIGRATION AND DECOMMISSION: ' + ca + ' capability for application ' + app + ' conversion to ' + fs;
        var sdPTmvp = 'MVP Date (IOC): ' + ca + ' capability for application ' + app + ' conversion to ' + fs;
        sd = true;
    }

    var modStart = new GlideDateTime();
    var modEnd = new GlideDateTime();
    var decomStart = new GlideDateTime();
    var decomEnd = new GlideDateTime();
    var mvpDate = false;
    var modS = false;
    var decomS = false;
    var decomE = false;


    //set vars for start and end dates
    if (source.u_mvp_start_date) {
        modStart = source.u_mvp_start_date + ' 00:00:00';
        modS = true;
    }
    if (source.u_mvp_date__ioc_) {
        modEnd = source.u_mvp_date__ioc_ + ' 00:00:00';
        mvpDate = true;
    }
    if (source.u_replacement_start_date) {
        decomStart = source.u_replacement_start_date + ' 00:00:00';
        decomS = true;
    }
    if (source.u_replacement_finish_end_date) {
        decomEnd = source.u_replacement_finish_end_date + ' 00:00:00';
        decomE = true;
    }
